@[simp]
theorem to_fun_eq_coe (f : ring_invo R) : f.to_fun = f :=
  rfl
#align to_fun_eq_coe to_fun_eq_coe
map_eq_zero_iff:
#print map_eq_zero_iff /-
@[simp]
theorem map_eq_zero_iff (f : ring_invo R) {x : R} : f x = 0 ↔ x = 0 :=
  f.to_ring_equiv.map_eq_zero_iff
#align map_eq_zero_iff map_eq_zero_iff
-/
involution:
@[simp]
theorem involution (f : ring_invo R) (x : R) : (f (f x).unop).unop = x :=
  f.involution' x
#align involution involution
coe_ring_equiv:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃+* » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ᵐᵒᵖ» -/
@[norm_cast]
theorem coe_ring_equiv (f : ring_invo R) (a : R) : (f : «expr ≃+* » R («expr ᵐᵒᵖ» R)) a = f a :=
  rfl
#align coe_ring_equiv coe_ring_equiv
